steps.name: Select the browsers as Chrome
Enter the urls as http://automationpractice.com
Click to signin link
Enter the usernames as someone@example.com
Enter the passwords as Password123
Click to login button
Click the T-shirt link in Title menu and select the Tshirt as Faded Short Sleeve T-shirts to order
Select the quantity as 2, Size as M and color as Blue
Click add to cart as selected the product
Click to proceed to summary
Click to proceed to address
Validate the delivery option and check the terms of service in shipping
Whether would you like do payment via bank or check as check and order the product
